{"tid":1562882,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"致每一位盡忠職守的消防及救護員","createTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T08:06:14.000Z","uid":47598,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2378de026c9dd569072dfce2cf9671df73ed02c1","tid":1562882,"uid":47598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red］致咁多位消防員同救護員:<br />\n大家唔同政治上既立場同政見我唔介意，但係呢一刻絕對係良知既判決時候，消防員一直係香港市民心中都係備受尊重既紀律部隊，因為你地每一個都盡忠職守，保護香港！加上你地一直都係默默做而不求一分回報，香港人係通通都記得！<br />\n你地辛辛苦苦建立咁耐既野，值得比班黑警拖累咩？佢地仲值得你地不惜一切咁維護佢地咩？唔好忘記，救人救火係你地既職責，由佢地阻止你地入地鐵站救人既一刻，你地既專業經已被徹底地被踐踏，你地仲要忍嗎？<br />\n勇敢企出黎啦，我地真.香港人會同你地每一位有良知既消防員同救護員同行！[/red]</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae5262846faa509d100c3d8b54f234c69c293af","tid":1562882,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T07:52:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"7d424699b427c17b38c6c41aaf5ac089555248c7","tid":1562882,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,